title: Eating Shit Doesn't Solve Your Worries
itunes:title: Eating Shit Doesn't Solve Your Worries
description:
Today I teach you why you can't keep eating through stress and worry. It never SOLVES it and it NEVER really comforts you. In this podcast I teach live and answer ALL the questions around how to quit thinking your overeating is somehow helping you.
